{
  "texts": [
    "Our in-depth error analysis offers more insight into recurring model failures.",
    "We provide a public leaderboard to encourage continuous updates.",
    "Researchers and practitioners can contribute new datasets or model results, extending FLAME beyond our initial contributions.",
    "By design, this effort explicitly welcomes peer review and invites ongoing collaboration.",
    "We present a holistic taxonomy for financial NLP tasks, detailing the financial domain scenario and categorizing benchmarking tasks."
  ]
